&lt;I am born now&gt; she thinks &lt;just as I am born anew with every breath... there is no restriction that I do not place with my own hand...&gt;<br>
Smiling she gets up, disturbing a fine white short-hair cat that was snoozing in the crook of her legs.<br>
&quot;Well hello, handsome!&quot; She spoils him with much petting as he gazes up at her with heavy-lidded eyes of bliss. &lt;I suppose I am still at Liani's&gt; she thinks, looking about the room... simple, clean, many plants, a statue of a naked young man holding a spear (!), a water basin and mirror... very peaceful and cozy! She gets out of bed and stretches to and fro... peeking at herself in the mirror occasionally.<br>
