&quot;Hey! How did you get in there, mister?&quot; She peers into the dark hallway as the cat bumps his head against her legs. A curving stairwell down... with a very vague scent of patchuli and govinda and... something else... wafting into the room. &lt;What kind of tricks has Liani built into this house of hers?&gt;<br>
